name: Frog's Feast!
description:
Ah, a peaceful day as a frog in the swamp...

Oh, whats that? A big bunch of delicious bugs!

I hope I don't get tired eating all of them...

Controls:

Just click anywhere and I will shoot my tongue towards that point to eat any bug there!

Eat as many bugs as you can before my energy runs out!
